T02TD1969E:109a-1: ya m'a ri tu no tanta badzra dhrik / bod skad du /
T02TD1969E:109a-2: rdo rje 'dzin pas gshin rje gshed po la bstod pa'i rgyud /
T02TD1969E:109a-3: byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1969E:109b-0: de nas 'og min gyi gnas btsun mo'i bha ga @109b la //
T02TD1969E:109b-1: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed rang gi che ba bstod cing bzhugs so //
T02TD1969E:109b-2: de'i tshe rdo rje 'dzin pas btsun mo'i bha ga rgyas par byas te /
T02TD1969E:109b-3: gshin rje gshed po la bstod pa //
T02TD1969E:109b-4: h'um khro bo'i rgyal po zhe sdang gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1969E:109b-5: rang bzhin spros bral chos kyi dbyings la gnas //
T02TD1969E:109b-6: mtshan ma'i rtog med rang bzhin lhun gyis grub //
T02TD1969E:109b-7: 'chi bdag sdang 'joms ye shes gnyis med sku //
T02TD1969E:109b-8: dri med rnam dag thugs rje shugs las skyes //
T02TD1969E:109b-9: 'bar ba'i sku mchog bcom ldan gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1969E:109b-10: longs spyod bde ba chen po gnyis med 'khril //
T02TD1969E:109b-11: kha sbyor 'dod chags skyon gyis ma gos shing //
T02TD1969E:109b-12: thugs rje'i thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul mdzad pa //
T02TD1969E:109b-13: drag po 'dul phyir mi bzad drag po'i gzugs //
T02TD1969E:109b-14: khro bo'i rgyal po gzhan gyis khyod mthong nas //
T02TD1969E:109b-15: ngo mtshar rab tu 'jigs shing 'bros par 'gyur //
T02TD1969E:109b-16: khyod kyi thugs ni zhe sdang 'chi bdag 'joms //
T02TD1969E:109b-17: nyon mongs bdud mdzad 'gro ba'i mgon po khyod //
T02TD1969E:109b-18: ma g-yos mi rtog chos kyi sku la gnas //
T02TD1969E:109b-19: rnam rtog dra ba gcod mdzad gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1969E:109b-20: zhe sdang thugs kyi rigs la phyag 'tshal lo /
T02TD1969E:109b-21: spros med chos kyi dbyings las ma g-yos kyang //
T02TD1969E:109b-22: zhe sdang drag pos gdul phyir 'bar ba'i sku //
T02TD1969E:109b-23: 'chi bdag gshin rje pho mo gdan du btang //
T02TD1969E:109b-24: ma he'i thog na zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum bzhugs //
T02TD1969E:109b-25: stobs ldan ma he drag brgyug lcags rmig can //
T02TD1969E:109b-26: aog yu 'bar zhing rva rno nyi ma'i gdan //
T02TD1969E:109b-27: khyod kyi sku ni char sprin lta bu ste //
T02TD1969E:109b-28: zhal gsum pa la phyag drug rnam par mdzes //
T02TD1969E:109b-29: mgo skyes kham pa sma ra gyen du 'greng //
T02TD1969E:109b-30: rigs bzhi'i klu dang phyag rgya lnga yis ni //
T02TD1969E:109b-31: khyod kyi dbu ni mdzes par brgyan pa yin //
T02TD1969E:109b-32: smin mtshams par ni mthong nas nges par 'jigs //
T02TD1969E:109b-33: me mdag lta bu'i spyan dgu gyen du bzlog / gyen 'bud shangs nas zhe sdang gdug pa'i sprul //
T02TD1969E:109b-34: khrag gis brlan pa'i zhal ni shin tu bgrad //
T02TD1969E:109b-35: mche ba zla tshes zang yag 'bar ba gtsigs //
T02TD1969E:109b-36: rngam pa'i h'um sgrogs ljags ni gyen du 'dril //
T02TD1969E:109b-37: sha za'i mgo bcad lus kyi rgyan du thogs //
T02TD1969E:109b-38: nga rgyal kun 'phrog mi thung 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD1969E:110a-2: shes rab gnyis med ral gri thabs kyis gdengs //
T02TD1969E:110a-3: las kyi dbyug pa dag gis 'chi bdag 'joms //
T02TD1969E:110a-4: nyon mongs bsreg mkhas phyag gis 'khor ba bsdigs //
T02TD1969E:110a-5: nyon mongs gcod mdzad shes rab dgra sta gdengs //
T02TD1969E:110a-6: log par lta ba bde ba chen por 'ching //
T02TD1969E:110a-7: rigs dang shes rab pha rol phyin par ldan //
T02TD1969E:110a-8: gsus pa che la thur du bshal ba dang //
T02TD1969E:110a-9: mtshams thung rngam chen khyod ni mthong bas 'jigs //
T02TD1969E:110a-10: gcan gzan rgan po stag gi na bzas brgyan //
T02TD1969E:110a-11: yan lag lnga ni klu lngas legs par dkris //
T02TD1969E:110a-12: zag pa med pa'i bde bas kun la khyab //
T02TD1969E:110a-13: bskal ba 'jigs pa'i me yi nang na bzhugs //
T02TD1969E:110a-14: rab tu mdzes pa'i sku 'bar 'od tshogs can //
T02TD1969E:110a-15: thabs dang shes rab bde bas gnyis med 'khril //
T02TD1969E:110a-16: rab brjid gshin rje gshed po'i sku mthong na //
T02TD1969E:110a-17: khro bo'i rgyal po gzhan gyi lag ca 'chor //
T02TD1969E:110a-18: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams kyang khyod la bstod //
T02TD1969E:110a-19: rngam pa'i 'khor tshogs rab tu 'jigs mdzad pa //
T02TD1969E:110a-20: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1969E:110a-21: 'khor lo bzhi yi bde ba khyod la gnas //
T02TD1969E:110a-22: dri med rnam dag gsung ni yang dag sgrogs //
T02TD1969E:110a-24: sngags kyis srid gsum gdug pa 'dul //
T02TD1969E:110a-25: rdo rje phag mo rab tu dgyes mdzad ma //
T02TD1969E:110a-26: ha ha bzhad pa'i dregs pas dgyes mdzad cing //
T02TD1969E:110a-27: gdug pa za byed rgyal ba'i gsung mchog la //
T02TD1969E:110a-28: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams kyis mgrin gcig bstod //
T02TD1969E:110a-29: rgyal ba gsung ba 'khor lo rnam par dag / mgon po gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1969E:110a-30: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'gro don mdzad //
T02TD1969E:110a-31: phrin las thogs pa med pa phyogs bcur khyab //
T02TD1969E:110a-32: las kyi 'khrul 'khor khyod kyis gcod mdzad cing //
T02TD1969E:110a-33: phrin las bzhi yi 'khor lo rdzogs mdzad pa //
T02TD1969E:110a-34: khro bo'i rgyal po zhe sdang gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1969E:110a-35: sku gsung rdzogs mdzad 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed //
T02TD1969E:110a-36: gdug pa za byed 'jam dpal gshin rje'i sku //
T02TD1969E:110a-37: phrin las mthar phyin khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02TD1969E:110a-38: gang zhig dus gsum dag tu 'di dag gis //
T02TD1969E:110a-39: rtog med gus pa sems kyis gang bstod pa //
T02TD1969E:110b-0: de ni rgyal ba thams cad bstod pas @110b na //
T02TD1969E:110b-1: che gcig gis ni gshin rje gshed 'drar 'gyur //
T02TD1969E:110b-2: rdo rje 'dzin pas gshin rje gshed po la bstod pa le'u'i rgyud las bstod pa'i le'u'o //
